sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as API
    participant Jira as Jira API
    participant DB as MySQL

    FE->>API: GET /api/tickets
    API->>Jira: searchTickets JQL
    Jira->>API: issues
    API->>DB: insertTicketIgnore
    API->>DB: getTicketsWithActions
    DB->>API: tickets + action_count
    API->>FE: count, data

    Note over FE,DB: Click ticket
    FE->>API: GET /api/tickets/:id
    API->>Jira: getTicketDetails
    Jira->>API: payload ADF comments
    API->>FE: ticketDetails
